{"tid":2065774,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marisa Tomei 後悔接演《蜘蛛俠》「最性感梅嬸」","createTime":"2020-06-15T22:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T11:11:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b3db7572062b0c42c378b94e4c80b5cb66150d8e","tid":2065774,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/0-1592213443.jpg?crop=0.498xw:0.947xh;0.00163xw,0.0124xh&amp;resize=640:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F0-1592213443.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0.498xw%3A0.947xh%3B0.00163xw%2C0.0124xh%26resize%3D640%3A%2A&h=016bf9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在歷年來各種版本的《蜘蛛人》（Spider-Man）電影中，漫威宇宙中由55歲瑪麗莎托梅（Marisa Tomei）飾演的「梅嬸」應該是最受歡迎的一個，電影中她和「小蜘蛛人」湯姆霍蘭德（Tom Holland）的互動總是充滿趣味，深受粉絲喜愛。不過瑪麗莎最近卻在專訪中透露，其實自己有點後悔接了「梅嬸」這個角色！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗莎托梅在最新專訪中向外媒透露，自從演了「梅嬸」之後，她的戲路就開始被定型成「媽媽」型的角色！<br />\n<br />\n像是她在今年的新作品《史泰登島國王》（The King of Staten Island）中，也是飾演主角的媽媽，這樣的「定型效應」讓還想嘗試更多不同類型角色的瑪麗莎不滿，因此對當初的決定感到後悔，她說到：「我真的很後悔開始了這條路，我總是覺得我可以演出各種不同的角色！」<br />\n<br />\n對角色受限感到失望，瑪麗莎也進一步表示：「我覺得每個演員都有著很多不同面向，但如果劇本的廣度受限，我們也只能繼續做下去，至少我已經盡力演到最好了。」<br />\n<br />\n從「梅嬸」的受歡迎程度看來，儘管瑪麗莎本人可能不太滿意，但粉絲們可是非常喜歡新版「梅嬸」啊！<br />\n<br />\n對自己的演藝事業很有想法的瑪麗莎，也透露她希望能演出像是幫派電影中的「蛇蠍美人」，或是愛情喜劇片裡的各種角色她也都很願意嘗試，她表示：「女人有太多不同的面向了，有好多角色能發揮！」<br />\n<br />\n儘管對自己的戲路受限感到失望，瑪麗莎近期也還是稍稍的透露了《蜘蛛人3》「梅嬸」的最新走向，表示下一集梅嬸會成為「社區組織者」，並在故事中佔有重要地位。<br />\n<br />\n而受到疫情影響《蜘蛛人3》延後到2021年才會上映，隨著《蜘蛛人：離家日》結尾將劇情推入新高潮，也讓人更期待「梅嬸」和「小蜘蛛人」的回歸！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/tw/celebrity/celebritynews/g32863759/spiderman-marisa-tomei-regert-aunt-may-character/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.harpersbazaar.com%2Ftw%2Fcelebrity%2Fcelebritynews%2Fg32863759%2Fspiderman-marisa-tomei-regert-aunt-may-character%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=21b74a17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.harpersbazaar.com/tw/celebrity/celebritynews/g32863759/spiderman-marisa-tomei-regert-aunt-may-character/</a>"},{"pid":"46782dbed4ee8095beca806845ff7c864a8e1c89","tid":2065774,"uid":194326,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:42:22.000Z","msg":"first world problem"},{"pid":"434a1d6d73555c4825b5160ed864e0b1e060cfd0","tid":2065774,"uid":105715,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:08:10.000Z","msg":"唔撚好玩啦，咁既老態做milf都益咗你啦"},{"pid":"022180a3d41a8465caa2033715baedc35b40778c","tid":2065774,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:10:56.000Z","msg":"睇唔出55歲"},{"pid":"d5069a00447ffd9fae2ac8fcd58b9ccb24fbed11","tid":2065774,"uid":175659,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"022180a3d41a8465caa2033715baedc35b40778c","tid":2065774,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:10:56.000Z","msg":"睇唔出55歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:23:04.000Z","msg":"以為85<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294b2dd91bb4bde7674883058f1b34c4c869bf48","tid":2065774,"uid":27251,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:53:08.000Z","msg":"就黎60歲仲想拍愛情片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賴得就賴"},{"pid":"9fd6c2ffc86d5a63b08912d72b3255e68ebe01f3","tid":2065774,"uid":202051,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"294b2dd91bb4bde7674883058f1b34c4c869bf48","tid":2065774,"uid":27251,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:53:08.000Z","msg":"就黎60歲仲想拍愛情片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賴得就賴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"係可以嘅，不過有幾多個人寫得出呢種劇本仲要高質<br />\n就算有又唔係一定要搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffba9a7f7336b2ca2013421003e68c8ae254d09","tid":2065774,"uid":27251,"like